    {
      "id": "1052427167724559",
      "score": 4,
      "review_title": "Just some bugs, plus mod menu issues",
      "review_description": "In my own personal opinion the 5 star reviews are total glaze, the game is really fun with not many issues just with some simple bugs that don’t really effect the gameplay that much. But a 5 star (the game is perfect) is way too far. The community is nice with it still not being super popular, moderators are nice. Although I don’t think the mods will read this comment but I have some suggestions to maybe help the game, first, adding more mods to the mod menu, there are around 5 mods in the mod menu and 2 of them don’t work and the “no tag freeze” in 90% scenarios is useless, meaning there are basically 2 mods that are good and work well. I also feel like a “no modded lobby” should exist, separating the people who use the mods from the people who don’t use it. That’s pretty much it for this review. For a summary, I just feel some of the bugs and mods can be fixed, community +moderators are nice, and more mods should be added too the mod menu. I genuinely think this game could average around 100 players daily if it is advertised more and keeps geting new content to the game.\n\nHave a nice day and I hope this review helped people looking for games and moderators looking for new things to add",
